channel.title: MkCrackelz -AutoPcTrainerV.1 Beta-
channel.description:
Well the title says it all. Its an auto Pest controller. It's pretty short and to the point when it comes to SCAR scripts, didn't have any time to make it extravagant, but its a work in progress. Good for pures, and just about any one who doesn't wanna waste their time trying to get void.
Please dont flame about how, the auto ban blows.. I KNOW. I made this script in like 10 minutes, and turns out that it works really good. Please give me feedback, tell me what you didn't like and what i should do better, and I'll fix it up for ye =)
and remember it's BETA.
Best Proggy Drop's AutoPCTrainerV.1Beta =============================================== User: stinkyboy5 PCRounds: 113 RunTime: 5 Hours, 6 Minutes and 6 Seconds ===============================================
Side note: I'm currently working on a Auto Soul Wars bot. If you have any ideas please pm me.
